{"data":{"page":{"id":"74996b3e-556a-5cbf-be4a-9b546333d8ea","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://www.yonococino.com/blog/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch website</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/16c613711dee67600ea94c8547aab8c8/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/16c613711dee67600ea94c8547aab8c8/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/16c613711dee67600ea94c8547aab8c8/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/16c613711dee67600ea94c8547aab8c8/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/16c613711dee67600ea94c8547aab8c8/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>As part of my involvement in the <a href=\"http://iweekend.org/en\">iWeekend event</a>, I helped to build the selected project: Yo No Cocino, an aggregator of restaurants and other food related businesses with an online ordering process and a delivery system.</p>\n<p>I helped to build the blog using Wordpress and a custom theme.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2009-11-16"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Yo no cocino","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/yonococino/","source":"work"}}